<figureCitation box="[982,1054,1459,1480]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="22.[197,229,1662,1681]" captionTargetBox="[176,658,946,1639]" captionTargetId="figure-560@22.[173,659,941,1642]" captionTargetPageId="22" captionText="Fig. 10. Known collection localities of New Zealand Sagola species. S. waipouaensis: black circles; S. brouni: triangles; S. plentyensis: black squares." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4907769" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4907769/files/figure.png" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Fig. 10</figureCitation>
